Hartford Financial Services Group
Inc. (HIG) , the insurer selling life units, hired Jac McLean as head
of distribution for the mutual-funds business.  McLean, 43, worked most recently as head of U.S. retail and
offshore sales at  Eaton Vance Corp. (EV) , according to a Business
Wire statement today from Hartford, which is based in the
Connecticut city of the same name.  To contact the reporter on this story:
